OL,4,CIllinois becomes first state to mandate
OL,5,Cteaching Asian American history
OL,6, Illinois has become the first US state
OL,7, to require teaching Asian American
OL,8, history in government-run schools.
OL,10,FAttacks on Asian Americans have been
OL,11,Frising since the start of the pandemic,
OL,12,Fand state officials say the law will
OL,13,Fcombat false stereotypes and bigotry.
OL,15,FSchools will be required to teach about
OL,16,Fthe contributions of Asian American
OL,17,Fcommunities to the development of the
OL,18,FUS, as well as civil rights history.
OL,20,FThe new mandate will take effect in
OL,21,Ftime for the 2022-2023 school year.
